msgstr "Hopefully in so doing your mind will find peace.” "

msgctxt "dn2:4.5"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, rājā māgadho ajātasattu vedehiputto tuṇhī ahosi. "
msgstr "But when he had spoken, the king remained silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs5, sc5
msgctxt "dn2:5.1"
msgid "Aññataropi kho rājāmacco rājānaṃ māgadhaṃ ajātasattuṃ vedehiputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Another of the king’s ministers said to him, "

msgctxt "dn2:5.2"
msgid "“ayaṃ, deva, pakudho kaccāyano saṅghī ceva gaṇī ca gaṇācariyo ca ñāto yasassī titthakaro sādhusammato bahujanassa rattaññū cirapabbajito addhagato vayoanuppatto. "
msgstr "“Sire, Pakudha Kaccāyana leads an order and a community, and teaches a community. He’s a well-known and famous religious founder, regarded as holy by many people. He is of long standing, long gone forth; he is advanced in years and has reached the final stage of life. "

msgctxt "dn2:5.3"
msgid "Taṃ devo pakudhaṃ kaccāyanaṃ payirupāsatu. "
msgstr "Let Your Majesty pay homage to him. "

msgctxt "dn2:5.4"
msgid "Appeva nāma devassa pakudhaṃ kaccāyanaṃ payirupāsato cittaṃ pasīdeyyā”ti. "
msgstr "Hopefully in so doing your mind will find peace.” "

msgctxt "dn2:5.5"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, rājā māgadho ajātasattu vedehiputto tuṇhī ahosi. "
msgstr "But when he had spoken, the king remained silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs6, sc6
msgctxt "dn2:6.1"
msgid "Aññataropi kho rājāmacco rājānaṃ māgadhaṃ ajātasattuṃ vedehiputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Another of the king’s ministers said to him, "

#. VAR: sañcayo → sañjayo (bj, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: belaṭṭhaputto → velaṭṭhaputto (s1-3) | bellaṭṭhiputto (pts1)
msgctxt "dn2:6.2"
msgid "“ayaṃ, deva, sañcayo belaṭṭhaputto saṃghī ceva gaṇī ca gaṇācariyo ca ñāto yasassī titthakaro sādhusammato bahujanassa rattaññū cirapabbajito addhagato vayoanuppatto. "
msgstr "“Sire, Sañjaya Belaṭṭhiputta leads an order and a community, and teaches a community. He’s a well-known and famous religious founder, regarded as holy by many people. He is of long standing, long gone forth; he is advanced in years and has reached the final stage of life. "

msgctxt "dn2:6.3"
msgid "Taṃ devo sañcayaṃ belaṭṭhaputtaṃ payirupāsatu. "
msgstr "Let Your Majesty pay homage to him. "

